==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Primeval
<hw>Pri*me"val</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>primaevus</ets>; <ets>primus</ets> first + <ets>aevum</ets> age.
See <er>Prime</er>, <pos>a.</pos>, <ets>and</ets> <er>Age</er>.]</ety>
<def>Belonging to the first ages; pristine; original; primitive;
primary; <as>as, the <ex>primeval</ex> innocence of man</as>.</def>
⟦ldquo⟧This is the forest <xex>primeval</xex>.⟦rdquo⟧
<rj><au>Longfellow.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>From chaos, and <qex>primeval</qex> darkness, came Light.</q>
<rj><qau>Keats.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Primevally</ent>⟦br⟧
